caption.text:
Happy 21st birthday AMSA-Indonesia!

The day i went to medical school, i had some thoughts in my mind, some of them were "i want to have tons of friends all over the world, i want to go there, there and there, i want to meet great people". With these thoughts popping in my mind over and over and over again, i began to look for an organization which fits me. Shortly after, i discovered an organization called AMSA and i made one of the best decision in my life: being part of them. I am very thankful, to AMSA-Indonesia, for giving me opportunities to develop myself, for giving me lots of invaluable friends, for giving me chance of working with great people scattered all over Indonesia, and for everything. I'm wishing all the best for AMSA-Indonesia. Also, i hope AMSA-Indonesia will give a bigger impact to the society as well as the member.

#VivaAMSA
#AMSAIndonesia
#AMSAXXI
#AMSAMoments
